- Beloved!

39:55.360 --> 39:58.062
Praise God! Ha ha!

39:58.163 --> 40:00.431
Beloved, now,
these saints of the church,

40:00.532 --> 40:02.266
Claire and Horace Jackson,

40:02.367 --> 40:05.036
who we all know just won
themselves that Powerball...

40:05.137 --> 40:07.071
Hallelujah!

40:07.172 --> 40:09.040
...who could have run off this weekend

40:09.141 --> 40:12.576
and blown it all on riches
that rust and fade away,

40:12.678 --> 40:15.379
but instead they came to
church like regular folk

40:15.480 --> 40:18.449
to drop a deposit
into the bank of eternity

40:18.550 --> 40:20.818
to the tune of $50,000!

40:20.919 --> 40:24.588
Praise God! Boom!

40:24.690 --> 40:27.258
Dropping like the atomic bomb!

40:27.359 --> 40:29.260
- Boom!
- Boom!

40:29.361 --> 40:31.062
Right into the pit of Hell.

40:31.163 --> 40:32.897
- Boom!
- Boom!

40:32.998 --> 40:37.399
Breaking down those walls
and setting captives free!

40:37.501 --> 40:40.471
- Boom!
- Boom!

40:40.572 --> 40:44.475
The Lord God of hosts proclaims,

40:44.576 --> 40:48.290
"You're not going to keep my
saints bound up down there!"

40:48.391 --> 40:51.682
Not today, Satan! Not today!

40:51.783 --> 40:53.484
Praise God!

40:53.585 --> 40:56.087
Oh, yes!

40:56.188 --> 40:57.421
Amen!

41:01.827 --> 41:03.094
Church good?

41:03.195 --> 41:04.795
Listen, that girl you mentioned,

41:04.896 --> 41:07.098
the one from the church
who gave her statement?

41:07.571 --> 41:09.538
