force can get me her name?

41:11.169 --> 41:12.174
I can ask,

41:12.276 --> 41:14.676
but you got to promise me something.

41:16.320 --> 41:18.654
You won't run away
like you did last time.

41:20.979 --> 41:22.146
I promise.

